### Assistant [2026-07-05T13:44:06.290Z]
PR opened: https://github.com/yosefsha/copypaste/pull/12

**Root cause**: `PastesEdgeStack` creates the S3 bucket and CloudFront `/static/*` behavior but never uploads `src/copypaste/static/*` into it — the bucket was empty, so CloudFront returned 403 for `style.css`/`pygments.css`.

**Fix**: added `aws_s3_deployment.BucketDeployment` to sync the static files in and auto-invalidate the `/static/*` CloudFront cache on deploy. `cdk synth PastesEdgeStack` passes.

Once you merge, you'll need to redeploy (`cdk deploy PastesEdgeStack` or `--all`) against `mypersonalprofile` to actually push the assets up and fix the live site.

